# Images for Documentation

This folder contains images and screenshots for the AccMan documentation.

## File Organization

- `screenshots/` - Application screenshots
- `diagrams/` - Architecture and flow diagrams
- `icons/` - Icons and logos
- `ui/` - UI mockups and designs

## Image Guidelines

- Use PNG format for screenshots
- Use SVG format for diagrams and icons when possible
- Optimize images for web (compress before adding)
- Use descriptive filenames (e.g., `dashboard-overview.png`)
- Keep images under 1MB when possible

## Usage in Markdown

```markdown
![Alt text](assets/images/screenshot.png)
```

For GitHub Pages, images will be accessible at:
`https://yourusername.github.io/AccMan/assets/images/filename.png`